---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
    title="Container Queries"
    description="Container queries and component-driven responsiveness."
>
    <section class="site-hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">Modern CSS</p>

        <h1>
            Container queries
        </h1>

        <p class="intro">
            Container queries allow components to respond to their own layout
            constraints instead of viewport assumptions.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-block">
<pre><code>@container (min-width: 40rem) {
    .product-card {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
}</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="content-block">
        <h2>
            Architecture impact
        </h2>

        <ul>
            <li>improves component portability</li>
            <li>reduces layout coupling</li>
            <li>supports reusable UI systems</li>
            <li>improves responsive architecture</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</DocsLayout>
